{"tid":2229814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩被爆曾當眾辱罵習近平「狗崽子」","createTime":"2020-10-04T15:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T15:18:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":582,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"246b3fa92897d2749eda4116d947c1aed2703dea","tid":2229814,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"北韓領袖金正恩日前致電國家主席習近平，祝賀新中國成立71周年。金正恩在賀電中聲稱積極發展朝中友誼並與中國同行。不過， 最近卻有一名來自北韓的青年爆料，中國和北韓的關係實際上並不如外界所認為的和諧友好。南韓在選擇接受佈署美軍的薩德系統（THAAD，終端高空防禦系統）前，與中國曾維持一段頗親密的關係，當時習近平甚至不顧「血盟之邦」北韓的感受出訪南韓，會晤時任南韓總統朴槿惠，氣得金正恩當著北韓軍人面前大罵習近平是「狗崽子」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.newtalk.tw/resize_action2/600/album/news/119/5abb18a5214ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.newtalk.tw%2Fresize_action2%2F600%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F119%2F5abb18a5214ab.png&h=84164cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-04/474534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-10-04%2F474534&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=7ecd5723\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-04/474534</a>"},{"pid":"7e87668cc0f6f09c0f3358758662b9fa4bde1558","tid":2229814,"uid":38904,"like":147,"dislike":3,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"金仔俾侵侵中出36Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梗係反雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750b37b0e9850795f7e5b084304f1dd3f87f407c","tid":2229814,"uid":34189,"like":452,"dislike":2,"score":450,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"金仔中文水平唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf025ce77d1f3bae928c2965719d9f5dd928923","tid":2229814,"uid":106604,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"狗崽子習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" 